  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>We've been providing unforgettable ski and snowboarding experiences for 90 years. Whether you're a loyal guest or have never booked with us before, let us find you an amazing Inghams holiday.</p>
<p>From luxury and spa hotels, all inclusive chalets to ski-in ski-out apartments all based in dynamic resorts offering the best for beginners, the ideal après locations to family friendly areas. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/5c6f2f5dfa2c4004b3e082a734fe1507" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5c6f2f5dfa2c4004b3e082a734fe1507}" class="c-btn">Accommodation options</a></p>
<p>We are certain that we have a holiday to suite your style. </p>
<p><em>Know when to go - find the best time to go on a skiing holiday to suit you: <a data-udi="umb://document/e0c616470b3c42db8e6ecca08307cca1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0c616470b3c42db8e6ecca08307cca1}" title="When to go">When to go skiing</a></em></p>
<p> </p>]]></bodyText>
